    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Cut your<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the<strong> chips </strong>to a baking tray and drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the chips are cooked through and crisp</p>",
